OL,3,CGovernment urged to review 'broken'
OL,4,Cdrug supply chain amid shortages
OL,6,FThe has been urged to carry out a
OL,7,Freview of the UK's "broken" medicine
OL,8,Fsupply chain after new research found
OL,9,Fthe has worsened the issue in recent
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FExperts have described shortages of
OL,13,Fthe likes of antibiotics and
OL,14,Fmedication for epilepsy as a "shocking
OL,15,Fdevelopment" that is putting pressure
OL,16,Fon patients, GPs and .
OL,18,FPharmacy leaders also warned they are
OL,19,Funable to plan ahead to support
OL,20,Fpatients due to a lack of
OL,21,Fcommunication with officials.
