OL,3,CGovernment urged to review 'broken'
OL,4,Cdrug supply chain amid shortages
OL,6,FResearch by think tank the Nuffield
OL,7,FTrust and academics, which was funded
OL,8,Fby the Health Foundation, highlighted
OL,9,F"underlying fragilities" in both the
OL,10,Fglobal and UK medicine supply chain.
OL,12,FIt said while problems in the UK were
OL,13,Fnot caused by Brexit, leaving the
OL,14,FEuropean Union (EU) has exacerbated
OL,15,Fthem. This is due to the fall in the
OL,16,Fvalue of sterling and the UK being
OL,17,Fremoved from EU supply chains.
