OL,3,CGovernment urged to review 'broken'
OL,4,Cdrug supply chain amid shortages
OL,6,FMark Dayan, Brexit programme lead at
OL,7,Fthe Nuffield Trust, said: "Officials
OL,8,Fin the UK have put in place a much
OL,9,Fmore sophisticated system to monitor
OL,10,Fand respond, and used extra payments
OL,11,Fto try to keep products flowing.
OL,13,F"But exiting the EU has left the UK
OL,14,Fwith several additional problems `
OL,15,Fproducts no longer flow as smoothly
OL,16,Facross the borders with the EU, and in
OL,17,Fthe long term our struggles to approve
OL,18,Fas many medicines might mean we have
OL,19,Ffewer alternatives available."
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOU{D@^O]
