OL,4,Cdrug supply chain amid shortages
OL,6,FThere is also a risk of the UK being
OL,7,Fleft out of EU measures to respond to
OL,8,Fshortages, such as bringing drug
OL,9,Fmanufacturing back to Europe, the
OL,10,Freport warned.
OL,12,FAnalysing freedom of information
OL,13,Frequests and public data on drug
OL,14,Fshortages, researchers found there is
OL,15,Fnow more than double the number of
OL,16,Fnotifications from drug companies
OL,17,Fwarning of impending shortages.
