OL,3,CGovernment urged to review 'broken'
OL,4,Cdrug supply chain amid shortages
OL,6,FHowever, the report also highlighted
OL,7,Fother unique issues for the UK market,
OL,8,Fincluding a change in demand to the
OL,9,Fmedicines prescribed by doctors.
OL,11,FOne example used was prescriptions for
OL,12,Fhormone replacement therapy (HRT) for
OL,13,Fmenopausal women, which increased by
OL,14,F40% in 2021/22.
OL,16,FResearchers also found that UK policy
OL,17,Fand NHS decisions on medicine pricing
OL,18,Fand financing has added to the issue.
