OL,6,FThe report warned that the health
OL,7,Fsector cannot rely on any formal
OL,8,Fchanges to the UK-EU relationship "any
OL,9,Ftime soon" and there are "steps well
OL,10,Fwithin the powers of the UK government
OL,11,Fto address these problems".
OL,13,FThese include better anticipating
OL,14,Fshortages and being more open about
OL,15,Fthem, as well as being wary of sudden
OL,16,Fsqueezes on cost driving instability.
