OL,6,FLouise Ansari, chief executive at
OL,7,FHealthwatch England, warned that
OL,8,F"shortages of vital medication can
OL,9,Fhave a detrimental impact on people's
OL,10,Fcondition, and their lives".
OL,12,F"We are calling on the government to
OL,13,Fcarry out a review of the medicine
OL,14,Fsupply chain to ensure medicine safety
OL,15,Fand resilience," she added.
OL,17,F"Where safe to do so and in
OL,18,Fcollaboration with patients, pharmacy
OL,19,Fteams should be given the flexibility
OL,20,Fto make changes to the medicines they
OL,21,Fdispense.
