OL,6,FDr Leyla Hannbeck, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe Association of Independent
OL,8,FMultiple Pharmacies (AIMp), said: "The
OL,9,Fmedicines supply chain is broken at
OL,10,Fevery level and unless the Department
OL,11,Fof Health reviews its processes and
OL,12,Fprocedures, we will never achieve the
OL,13,Fstability that will guarantee patients
OL,14,Ftheir prescription when they need it.
OL,16,F"Pharmacists spend hours every day
OL,17,Ftrying to source medicines for
OL,18,Fpatients and they are often out of
OL,19,Fpocket due to a broken reimbursement
OL,20,Fmechanism.
